snippet.title: Game Boy Longplay [063] Operation C
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played By: Waldimart

This game got its release as "Contra" in Japan and as "Probotector" in the PAL region, released 1991 by Konami. It contains similar gameplay to NES versions of "Contra" and "Super C". An all-time classic! -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
